"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 26}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "特斯拉转向全新组装工艺「 unbox 」，类似「组装乐高积木」，有望使生产成本减半，将带来哪些影响？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "特斯拉正逐渐转向一项名为「unbox（拆箱式）」新组装工艺，与传统产线的流水线作业方式不同，这一新工艺更类似「组装乐高积木」：汽车车身无需像以前一样在一条传送带上传送依次组装零部件，特斯拉计划在工厂的专用区域同时组装车辆的不同部分，最后将这些大型子组件装配在一起。与同等产量的传统汽车工厂相比，这项新工艺有望使生产成本减半，制造所需占地面积则减少 40% 以上。特斯拉正在转向全新组装工艺「unbox」"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-96803d29465fe343d7c063bbc6520245_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "105 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/651351182"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IjNDu5MaV67BrEAMaCTEwNzAyMjU2MSD2qq+wBjAAODdABXIJNjUxMzUxMTgyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "6_1712108397.866798", "card_id": "Q_650460938", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 16}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "古代战争中，步兵是如何经历长途奔袭还能保持作战能力的？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-b09fa8157aa838a0a93d827ba1ef7af2_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "88 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/650460938"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IjNDu5MaV67BrEAMaCTEwNjgyNDc0NCCOm5CwBjAAOCpABnIJNjUwNDYwOTM4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "7_1712108397.867017", "card_id": "Q_651296382", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87